Name: Black Designer Printed Cotton Gown with Kutchi Gamthi Lace & Kodi Work
Short description: Shine this Navratri in a designer printed gown crafted from premium cotton with Kutchi Gamthi lace and Kodi work. Featuring layered frill stitching and a 12-meter printed flair, perfect for Garba and festive celebrations.
Description:
Celebrate Navratri in style with this elegant designer printed gown. Made from heavy printed cotton, the gown is adorned with intricate Kutchi Gamthi lace and Kodi work, giving it a traditional yet stylish appeal. The 3-layer frill stitching and 12-meter printed flair create a beautiful flow, making every twirl on the dance floor memorable.

Designed with a fancy neckline and full-length cotton lining, this gown ensures comfort and elegance throughout your festive celebrations. Its 56-inch length provides a graceful silhouette suitable for Garba, Dandiya nights, and other festive occasions.

Ideal for women seeking a blend of comfort, style, and tradition, this gown is a must-have for your Navratri wardrobe.
